33
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,760
Where's your proof?

34
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:52,560
Based on Pei Qishan and Meng Lixian's

35
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,560
family disputes,

36
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,400
you want to make an arrest?

37
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:57,160
Do you know who Pei Qishan is?

38
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:58,440
Who is he?

39
00:01:59,040 --> 00:01:59,760
Master,

40
