75
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:28,320
(He can pursue his passions)

76
00:03:28,320 --> 00:03:29,520
(and follow his dreams.)

77
00:03:29,760 --> 00:03:31,600
(As for my divorce from Pei Qishan,)

78
00:03:32,040 --> 00:03:33,640
(I'll postpone it.)

79
00:03:33,640 --> 00:03:35,520
(At least during his childhood,)

80
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:37,520
(he should have a father.)

81
