102
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,160
Until today, I discovered

103
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,240
that child is actually alive.

104
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:26,400
Are you joking?

105
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:28,240
If the child truly lived,

106
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:30,400
would he be gone all these years?

107
00:05:33,960 --> 00:05:34,760
Look at this first.

108
00:05:53,160 --> 00:05:54,320
That's me?

109
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:56,960
Isn't the switched-at-birth trope

110
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:58,600
too cliche?

111
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:00,640
I respect you for age.

112
00:06:01,080 --> 00:06:02,400
But if you're messing with me,

113
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:04,200
then it's not fun.

114
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:06,760
Your so-called mother

115
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,040
had lost her fertility

116
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,640
before you were even conceived.

117
00:06:14,960 --> 00:06:16,960
This is Tang Ting's medical report

118
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:19,040
from sixteen years ago.

119
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:23,840
Do you think I'll believe

120
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:24,840
your fabricated stories?

121
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,800
I might fabricate lies,

122
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:29,640
but evidence doesn't.

123
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,640
I don't believe it.

124
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:34,840
Go investigate yourself.

125
00:06:35,640 --> 00:06:36,560
The evidence won't lie.

126
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:38,560
But kid,

127
00:06:38,960 --> 00:06:40,480
I hope you'll always stay vigilant

128
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:42,240
towards everyone, no matter when.

129
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:43,800
Look.

130
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:45,280
What has Pei Qishan done to you?

131
00:06:46,080 --> 00:06:47,840
Every single one of countless projects

132
00:06:47,840 --> 00:06:49,240
you've initiated was sabotaged

133
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,080
by Pei Qishan,

134
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:51,840
and reduced to worthless plans.

135
00:06:52,640 --> 00:06:53,600
He gave you money,

136
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,360
inflating your ambitions,

137
00:06:55,760 --> 00:06:57,160
and then made you realize

138
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:58,600
you're nothing but a useless one.

139
00:06:59,160 --> 00:07:01,000
Do you think he truly cares for you?

140
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:03,880
He's spent a lot of money on you.

141
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,520
But do you know

142
00:07:05,840 --> 00:07:07,400
since last century,

143
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:08,320
the wealth

144
00:07:08,320 --> 00:07:10,720
of the Meng family exceeded
the entire assets of Rong City?

145
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:12,720
Now it's all been

146
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:13,880
seized and squandered by him.

147
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,040
Even

148
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:17,720
your birth mother's death

149
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:20,400
was arranged by him.

150
