167
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:50,840
Was it me refusing?

168
00:08:53,520 --> 00:08:54,920
Or were there never any taken?

169
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:06,120
By the way, why didn't you
have more children?

170
00:09:07,520 --> 00:09:09,400
