172
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,000
Quite enviable.

173
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:21,640
That is not easy.

174
00:09:22,280 --> 00:09:23,360
It's fate.

175
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:28,640
